    "faq_9AXGPC": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "question_GYETCD": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "💧Toner",
            "answer": "<p>Toners are water-based liquids that balance your skin's pH after cleansing. They remove any remaining impurities and prepare your skin to better absorb the products that follow. Pacifica's toners are alcohol-free and packed with soothing botanicals!</p><p><strong>Pacifica Pro Tip:</strong></p><p>Apply toner with clean fingertips instead of cotton pads to avoid waste and ensure maximum product absorption!</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_hXFK9t": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "⚠️Parabens",
            "answer": "<p>Parabens are preservatives commonly used in cosmetics to prevent bacteria growth. However, they can disrupt hormone function and have been linked to various health concerns. That's why all Pacifica Beauty products are proudly paraben-free!</p><p><strong>Why We Say No:</strong></p><p>We believe in clean beauty that's good for you and the planet. Our natural preservation systems keep products fresh without compromising your health.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_hq7zVm": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "✨Glycolic Acid",
            "answer": "<p>Glycolic acid is an alpha hydroxy acid (AHA) derived from sugarcane. It's a superstar exfoliator that removes dead skin cells, unclogs pores, and stimulates collagen production for brighter, smoother skin.</p><p><strong>Why It's In Our Serums:</strong></p><p>Our glycolic acid formulations are carefully balanced to provide effective exfoliation without irritation. We pair it with soothing botanicals for the perfect glow without the harsh side effects!</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_fWUX3V": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "🧴Hyaluronic Acid",
            "answer": "<p>Hyaluronic acid is a moisture-binding ingredient that can hold up to 1000 times its weight in water. It plumps skin, reduces the appearance of fine lines, and provides intense hydration without feeling heavy.</p><p><strong>Hydration Hero: </strong>Our hyaluronic acid is derived from plant sources and formulated in multiple molecular weights to penetrate different skin layers for maximum hydration!</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_PpaYxB": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "☀️SPF",
            "answer": "<p>SPF (Sun Protection Factor) measures how well a sunscreen protects against UVB rays. It's the most important step in any skincare routine, as it prevents premature aging, hyperpigmentation, and skin cancer.</p><p><strong>Daily Essential: </strong>Pacifica's mineral sunscreens use non-nano zinc oxide for broad-spectrum protection that's reef-safe and gentle on sensitive skin. Apply as the final step in your morning routine!</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_biTBy4": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "🌱Niacinamide",
            "answer": "<p>Niacinamide (Vitamin B3) is a multitasking ingredient that strengthens the skin barrier, reduces inflammation, minimizes pores, and helps control oil production. It plays well with other ingredients and suits all skin types.</p><p><strong>Versatile Superstar: </strong>We include niacinamide in many of our formulations because it addresses multiple skin concerns simultaneously while being gentle enough for daily use!</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_nrWKne": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "🌿Antioxidants",
            "answer": "<p>Antioxidants neutralize free radicals (unstable molecules that damage skin cells and accelerate aging). Examples include vitamins C and E, green tea, and resveratrol. They're your skin's defense system against pollution and UV damage.</p><p><strong>Protection Power: </strong>Pacifica Beauty sources potent plant-based antioxidants that work synergistically to provide maximum protection and repair environmental damage!</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_PTcRpB": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "🦄 Pacifica Beauty",
            "answer": "<p>Beauty activists since 1996. For nearly 30 years, our grounding core value has always been compassion—for the planet, animals, and you. </p><p>Accessible prices, cruelty-free, with compassion for all.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
